metadata.name: The Merge 1 (Foundation)
metadata.description:
"it had finally happened and for the first time, they felt like their self..."

*entire process (no post-production or human edits) collaborated w/ AI technology, guided by dreamingdigitally

Twitter: @dreamingNFT
IG: dreamingdigitally

"The Merge" is a special collection for me as a Non-Binary Artist seeking to challenge preconceived boundaries of Body, Gender, Identity, Technology, Nature & more. I consider it a culmination of my lived experiences.
